branches_variant_requirements_chk.name: branches_variant_requirements_chk
branches_variant_requirements_chk.value: ("branches"."type" <> 'variant' OR ("branches"."forked_from_version_id" IS NOT NULL AND "branches"."forkset_id" IS NOT NULL))

branches_stream_parent_requires_fork_chk.name: branches_stream_parent_requires_fork_chk
branches_stream_parent_requires_fork_chk.value: (NOT ("branches"."type" = 'stream' AND "branches"."is_main" = false AND "branches"."parent_branch_id" IS NOT NULL) OR "branches"."forked_from_version_id" IS NOT NULL)

versions_revert_link_chk.name: versions_revert_link_chk
versions_revert_link_chk.value:
(("versions"."kind" <> 'revert') OR "versions"."reverted_version_id" IS NOT NULL)
             AND (("versions"."kind" = 'revert') OR "versions"."reverted_version_id" IS NULL)

versions_integration_link_chk.name: versions_integration_link_chk
versions_integration_link_chk.value:
(("versions"."kind" <> 'integration') OR "versions"."applied_from_branch_id" IS NOT NULL)
             AND (("versions"."kind" = 'integration') OR "versions"."applied_from_branch_id" IS NULL)
